### Test Subscription API Endpoints
### Make sure to replace {token} with actual JWT token

@baseUrl = https://localhost:7000/api
@token = your_jwt_token_here

### 1. Get all subscription types (public endpoint)
GET {{baseUrl}}/subscription-types
Content-Type: application/json

### 2. Get active subscription types (public endpoint)
GET {{baseUrl}}/subscription-types/active
Content-Type: application/json

### 3. Get subscription type by ID (public endpoint)
GET {{baseUrl}}/subscription-types/1
Content-Type: application/json

### 4. Get subscription type by code (public endpoint)
GET {{baseUrl}}/subscription-types/code/FREE
Content-Type: application/json

### 5. Subscribe to a subscription plan (requires authentication)
POST {{baseUrl}}/subscription/subscribe
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "subscriptionTypeId": 2,
    "description": "Upgrading to Basic plan"
}

### 6. Get current subscription (requires authentication)
GET {{baseUrl}}/subscription/current
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7. Get subscription history (requires authentication)
GET {{baseUrl}}/subscription/history
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8. Cancel current subscription (requires authentication)
POST {{baseUrl}}/subscription/cancel
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 9. Test AI limit check (requires authentication)
GET {{baseUrl}}/usage-tracking/status/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 10. Test AI request with limit check (requires authentication)
POST {{baseUrl}}/ai/gemini-1.5
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "question": "What is the capital of Vietnam?",
    "subject": "Geography"
}

### 11. Add balance to user account (requires authentication)
POST {{baseUrl}}/balance/add
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "amount": 100000,
    "description": "Adding balance for testing"
}

### 12. Get user balance (requires authentication)
GET {{baseUrl}}/balance
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
